{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800580/extras/mr_tomato_adventures_logo.png?t=1736888453\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embark on an epic adventure to restore peace to the Fruit Kingdom!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Traverse through challenging levels, face unique enemies, and solve intriguing puzzles to defeat the Legumes. Use special abilities and take down the evil King Cabbage!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800580/extras/characters.png?t=1736888453\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Features:</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Classic 2D Platformer:</strong> Experience a platformer inspired by the classics, featuring responsive controls and fun mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Boss Battles:</strong> Test your skills against unique bosses, each with distinct patterns and attacks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Funny and Engaging Story:</strong> Follow Mr. Tomato on his mission to prove that, despite appearances, he is a fruit and can be a hero against the evil vegetables.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Pixel Art Visuals:</strong> A vibrant and detailed world crafted in retro pixel art.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Variety of Enemies:</strong> Fight against a wide range of evil vegetables and discover their weaknesses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Do you have what it takes to restore order and show that a tomato can be a hero too?</strong></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800580/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736888453","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2800580/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736888453","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/st